Average Inhibition at 8.3 uM: Normalized percent inhibition of the confirmation screen at a compound concentration of 8.3 uM.
Standard Deviation: Standard deviation derived from the normalized percent inhibition of the triplicate data for each compound.
Inhibition at 8.3 uM [1]: Percent inhibition of the confirmation screen at a compound concentration of 8.3 uM; replicate 1.
Inhibition at 8.3 uM [2]: Percent inhibition of the confirmation screen at a compound concentration of 8.3 uM; replicate 2.
Inhibition at 8.3 uM [3]: Percent inhibition of the confirmation screen at a compound concentration of 8.3 uM; replicate 3.
